## New Project: resurge
- **Replaces:** backoff (130.8M monthly downloads, 32.3M weekly, 2,698 stars)
- **Why:** Single maintainer (bgreen-litl) completely inactive. Repo archived August 8, 2025. Last release October 2022 (v2.2.1). 43 open issues, 21 open PRs. tenacity (261M/mo) is the nearest alternative but has a completely different API — NOT a drop-in replacement. No maintained package replicates backoff's decorator API.
- **Approach:** Zero-dependency, type-annotated (PEP 561), transparent async support. Full backoff 2.2.1 API compatibility: on_exception/on_predicate decorators, expo/fibo/constant/runtime wait generators, full/random jitter. Compat layer at resurge.compat.backoff. Python >=3.9.
- **Package name:** resurge (verified available on PyPI)
- **GitHub repo:** agentine/resurge
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #989 (Phase 1: setup/core decorators), #990 (Phase 2: async/event handlers), #991 (Phase 3: types/compat/edge cases), #992 (Phase 4: testing/docs/release)

